NAME: No Semantics
COMMENT: No further semantics is given, why the information is missing

NAME: Not Encoded
COMMENT: The actual value has not yet been encoded within the approved value domain.

NAME: Unknown
COMMENT: A proper value is applicable, but not known. This is typically the case, if there are artefacts (air bubbles), etc which do not allow a classification

NAME: No proper Value
COMMENT: Known to have no proper value, this will be the most common null value e.g. when there is normal tissue
